These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
City: boston, venice, rome, hannover
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, rugby, tennis
1. the person traveling to rome is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is rowing##2
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
4. the person who's sport is rowing is not the person traveling to rome##6
5. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to boston##5
6. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| City   | hannover  | boston | rome | venice  |
| Sport   | biathlon | rugby   | tennis  | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, tomato, watermelon, zucchini
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, thriller, comedy, animation
1. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the person watching animation movies##8
2. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the right of the person eating zucchini##5
3. the person eating grapes is the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating grapes and the person eating tomato##2
5. the person eating tomato is somewhere between the person eating watermelon and the person watching western movies##7
6. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
7. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the person watching western movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | watermelon | tomato          | zucchini | grapes     |
| Movie-Genre    | comedy      | animation | western | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
House: cottage, palace, farmhouse, victorian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, family, superhero
1. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the farmhouse house##8
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
3. the palace house is on the right of the cottage house##1
4. the palace house is in an even position##4
5. the victorian house is on the far left or far right##3
6. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
7. the victorian house is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| House           | cottage | palace | farmhouse     | victorian |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | superhero   | adventure | family    |

