.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, pomegranate, apricot, grapes
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, handball, rugby
1. the person eating grapes is somewhere between the person eating peach and the person eating pomegranate##7
2. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
3. the person eating grapes is somewhere between the person eating apricot and the person eating peach##7
4. the person eating apricot is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person eating pomegranate and the person who's sport is cycling##7
6. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
7. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Food   | pomegranate   | apricot | grapes | peach    |
| Sport         | climbing | rugby   | handball   | cycling |

