2. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
5. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
6. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the person traveling to colone##8
7. the person eating pineapple is the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | kiwi  | lettuce |
| City   | colone   | hamburg         | venice | boston |

