.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, chinchilla, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, rowing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the owner of the bird##8
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the owner of the mouse and the person who's sport is rowing##7
3. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##8
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the owner of the bird##8
6. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
8. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Pet   | bird      | chinchilla | hamster | mouse   |
| Sport      | badminton | rowing | volleyball  | cricket |

