3. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person eating garlic##7
5. the person eating carrot is not to the right of the person eating radish##8
6. the person eating radish is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person eating carrot##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
