.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, indie, pop
City: rome, paris, san-francisco, prague
1. the fan of classical is between the fan of pop and the person traveling to rome##2
2. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
4. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
5. the person traveling to paris is the person traveling to paris##1
6. the fan of indie is not the person traveling to san-francisco##6
7. the fan of pop is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
8. the person traveling to rome is not to the left of the person traveling to paris##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | classical | indie | dubstep |
| City     | prague | paris       | rome  | san-francisco    |

