.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, librarian, manager, writer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, d&b, folk, electronic
1. the writer is between the fan of d&b and the fan of folk##2
2. the fan of hip-hop is not the librarian##6
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the chef##1
4. the manager is not to the right of the chef##8
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the chef##3
6. the fan of d&b is not to the right of the fan of hip-hop##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Job         | manager | chef      | writer   | librarian  |
| Music-Genre   | electronic    | d&b | hip-hop | folk |

