.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ivory, chestnut, turquise
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, quad-bike, scooter
1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
2. the person who likes chestnut is somewhere to the right of the person who likes turquise##5
3. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
4. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the person who likes turquise##8
5. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person who likes chestnut##8
6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| Color   | fuchsia     | turquise | chestnut | ivory |
| Transport     | quad-bike | scooter  | car    | boat   |

