2. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the victorian house##8
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the modern house##5
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left or far right##3
5. the cottage house is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
6. the victorian house is on the far left##1
7. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
