.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, thriller, martial-arts, sports
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, ice-hockey, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person watching sports movies is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person watching thriller movies##7
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
8. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | thriller         | martial-arts    | documentary       |
| Sport      | handball | skateboarding | biathlon | ice-hockey |

