2. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
4. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
5. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Pet   | bird     | snake | chinchilla        | turtle       |
| Hobby      | drawing | collecting  | card-games | magic-tricks |

