The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, indie, country, hip-hop
 1. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan of country##5
 2. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the person eating grapefruit is the fan of country##1
 4. the fan of country is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
 5. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the fan of indie is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 7. the fan of indie is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the fan of country##8
 9. the fan of indie is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
10. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the fan of disco##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | papaya    | watermelon | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Music-Genre   | disco | hip-hop  | country     | indie    |

