.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, avocado, grapefruit, peas
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, skateboarding, weightlifting, basketball
1. the person eating grapefruit is the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is not to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is the person eating peas##1
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
6. the person eating avocado is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person eating peas##2
7. the person eating grapefruit is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food    | peas        | avocado | asparagus | grapefruit |
| Sport   | basketball | weightlifting | skateboarding   | tennis    |

