.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, hedgehog
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, amaryllis, zinnia, dahlia
1. the person who growsamaryllis is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person who growsdahlia##8
4. the owner of the hamster is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who growsballoon-flower##7
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person who growszinnia is between the person who growsdahlia and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog | chinchilla | hamster |
| Flower   | amaryllis | dahlia      | zinnia     | balloon-flower     |

 